ness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17537,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/09\/tasbih-tahmid-33-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":28171,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Glorify Allah 33 times after every prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The poor emigrants came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cThe wealthy have taken the highest degrees and blessed ranks!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHow is that?\u201d They said, \u201cThey pray as we pray, they fast as we fast, they give in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32274,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/18\/doors-of-khayr-plentiful\/","url_meta":{"origin":28171,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Doors of virtuous good deeds are plentiful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no soul in the son of Adam but that charity is due upon it on every day the sun rises.\u201d It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, from what can we give in charity?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"